metadata.name: Eucalyptus #1
metadata.description:
Eucalyptus #1 is a 1/20 NFT in the Floral Abstractions Editions collection by [florintintin](https://www.instagram.com/florintintin/).

##Floral Abstractions
Floral Abstractions is a body of work where florintintin uses dynamic scanning techniques and an Impossible Lab printer to create surrealistic polaroids of dying flowers.
